headline: Is Weyerhaeuser (WY) Pricing Fair After Mixed Share Performance This Year?
summary: If you are wondering whether Weyerhaeuser is currently priced attractively or if the share price already reflects what you are paying for, this article walks through the key valuation checks investors usually consider. The stock last closed at US$26.75, with returns of 0.4% over the past week, a 1.1% decline over the last month, 12.4% year to date, and a 6.7% decline over the past year, so the recent performance has been mixed.
